George Kirby and 91-year-old Doreen Luckie from Eastbourne, East Sussex, will marry after first getting together 27 years ago in 1988 . 
  George, currently 102, proposed on Valentine's Day and will marry for the third time on June 13 . 
  On their wedding day, the pair will have a combined age of 195 years and 281 days . 
  They will also be the UK's most elderly groom at 103 . 
 